<#
.SYNOPSIS
	This script does really cool stuff

.DESCRIPTION
	This script uses a combination of MS Graph and Azure AD modules to export a detailed report of client applications from a tenant

.PARAMETER ClientName
	This is the name of the client.

.PARAMETER Application
	The application to check.

.PARAMETER ShowHidden
	Optional switch to show hidden applications

.EXAMPLE
	Get-ClientApplications.ps1 -ClientName Contoso -Application TestApplication -ShowHidden

.NOTES
	Author: John Smith
	Date:   January 1, 2023
	Tags: 	#IntunePortal, 	#CloudManager, #FilePermissions
#>